<%= stylesheet_link_tag "back-ab-team-col-new", :media => "all"  %>   
<% @title = "About CGT Page Back - New About Our Work Team Column" -%>
<% @header = "About CGT Page Back - New About Our Work Team Column" -%>
<div id="operate-mgt">
  <div id="operate-intro">
    <h3>Information About Our Work Team Column</h3>
    <p>The content is only text. The font size is 14px, and the color is blue. The size of the display box is 290x380px. 
    <p>In the column, at most, there are 2 paragraphes in it. In one paragraph case, it can include about 960 letters; In two paragraphes case, it can contain about 870 letters.  If the input is longer than the limit, the rest will be cut. Please pay attention to it.
    <p>After you input the new content, then it will replace your old one that will be changed. </p>
  </div><!-- end #operate-intro -->

  <div id="operate-area">
    <h3>New About Our Work Team Column</h3>
    
    <div id="operate-new">
      <% form_for :about,@about,:url => { :action => "create_team_col",:id => @team_col.id }, :html => { :method => :post } do |f| %>
        <div class="word">
          <p>New Comment:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 220 letters.)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="message">
          <%= f.text_area :content %>
        </div>
        <div class="word">
          <p>New Author:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 40 letters.)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <%= f.text_field :author %>
        </div>
        <div class="word">
          <p>New Admin:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 40 letters.)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <input name="Admin" type="text" class="input" maxlength=40 size=50 />
        </div>
        <div class="div">
          <p>
            <%= f.submit "New Content" ,:popup => "New Content Has Been Successfully Input!" %>
          </p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>    <!-- End #operate-new -->

    <div id="operate-buttons">
      <ul>
        <li><%= link_to "Back" ,:action => "team_col"%></li>
      </ul>
    </div>  <!-- End #operate-bottons -->

  </div>   <!-- end #operate-area -->
    
</div>  <!-- end #operate-mgt -->
